#: ../../manual/sculpt_paint/weight_paint/hide_mask.rst:69
msgid "Face Selection masking."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/sculpt_paint/weight_paint/hide_mask.rst:71
msgid ""
"The *Face Selection masking* allows you to select faces and limit the "
"weight paint tool to those faces, very similar to Vertex selection "
"masking."
msgstr ""
"Le mode *Face Selection masking* vous permet de sélectionner des faces et"
" limiter l'outil *weight paint* à ces faces, très semblable à *Vertex "
"selection masking*."

#: ../../manual/sculpt_paint/weight_paint/hide_mask.rst:76
msgid "Hide/Unhide Faces"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/sculpt_paint/weight_paint/hide_mask.rst:80
msgid "Hidden faces."
msgstr "Faces cachées."

#: ../../manual/sculpt_paint/weight_paint/hide_mask.rst:82
msgid ""
"You also can hide selected faces as in Edit Mode with the keyboard "
"Shortcut :kbd:`H`, then paint on the remaining visible faces and finally "
"unhide the hidden faces again by using :kbd:`Alt-H`."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez aussi cacher des faces sélectionnées comme en *Mode Édition* "
"avec le raccourci clavier :kbd:`H`, puis peignez sur les faces visibles "
"restantes et finalement réafficher les faces cachées en utilisant "
":kbd:`Alt-H`."

#: ../../manual/sculpt_paint/weight_paint/hide_mask.rst:88
msgid "Hide/Unhide Vertices"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/sculpt_paint/weight_paint/hide_mask.rst:90
msgid ""
"You cannot directly hide selected faces in vertex mask selection mode. "
"However, you can use a trick:"
msgstr ""
"Vous ne pouvez pas cacher directement les faces en mode *Vertex mask "
"selection*. Cependant vous pouvez utiliser une astuce :"

#: ../../manual/sculpt_paint/weight_paint/hide_mask.rst:93
msgid "First go to Face selection mask mode."
msgstr "D'abord entrez en mode *Face selection mask*."

#: ../../manual/sculpt_paint/weight_paint/hide_mask.rst:94
msgid ""
"Select the areas you want to hide and then hide the faces (as explained "
"above)."
msgstr ""
"Sélectionnez les zones que vous souhaitez cacher et ensuite cachez les "
"faces (comme expliqué ci-dessus)."

#: ../../manual/sculpt_paint/weight_paint/hide_mask.rst:95
msgid "Switch back to Vertex Selection mask mode."
msgstr "Retournez en mode *Vertex Selection mask*."

#: ../../manual/sculpt_paint/weight_paint/hide_mask.rst:97
msgid "Now the vertices belonging to the hidden Faces will remain hidden."
msgstr "À présent les sommets appartenant aux Faces cachées vont rester cachés."

